      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Security Events Dashboard (Phase 2B)\n\nThis dashboard focuses on **security-relevant events**:\n- UFW (firewall) - blocked connections\n- sudo (privilege escalation) - command execution\n- sshd (SSH auth) - login attempts and auth events\n- cron (scheduled tasks) - job execution\n\n**Use case**: Security monitoring, audit trails, and threat detection\n\n**Security domains**: Firewall, Authentication, Privilege Escalation, Task Execution"
